    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sylvester and the entity of Dust is an Action RPG game with Rogue Lite mecamism. Embark on an epic adventure in stunning 3D isometric view, powered by the  graphical power of Unreal Engine 5.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dive into a visually striking world  where low-poly models meet cartoon aesthetics in an innovative 3D isometric design.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As Sylvester, face your destiny across:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40+ intense levels spanning 3 diverse biomes,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25 unique enemy types to outsmart and overpower,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 intimidating bosses,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >28 powerful weapons to master and boosters,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rogue-lite elements : Random weapon drops and boosters keep every run fresh, Permanent death raises the stake.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to conquer the Entity of Dust in this unforgiving action-RPG experience ?</strong></p>",
